0.04   2008-04-18

- This module did not respcet the init_arg attribute setting, and used
  the attribute name instead. Reported by Matt Trout. RT #34507.


0.03   2007-11-20

- Require Moose 0.26, since that's first version to offer init_meta(),
  apparently.


